// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3056 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: d0e54bd6-88a4-5ca5-8127-f4b23133eabc

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
